sentences: The group was composed of nine members: Jun, Euijin, Ko Ho-jung, Feeldog, Marco, Ji Han-sol, Daewon, Kijung, and Chan.
Their debut album, Boyhood, was released on April 7, 2018.
UNB ended their activities on January 27, 2019.
Prior to The Unit, all the members were actively involved in the entertainment industry: Feeldog debuted in 2012 as a member of Big Star.
